---
layout: base.njk
title: "Blog | Feng"
description: "Physics deep-dives, coding experiments, and reflections on the intersections of art and literature."
canonicalUrl: "https://fqian5.github.io/blog/"
bodyClass: "font-body text-on-surface selection:bg-secondary-container"
---
<div class="dust-mote" style="top: 10%; left: 20%;"></div>
<div class="dust-mote" style="top: 40%; left: 80%;"></div>
<div class="dust-mote" style="top: 70%; left: 15%;"></div>
<div class="dust-mote" style="top: 25%; left: 50%;"></div>
<div class="dust-mote" style="top: 85%; left: 60%;"></div>

<main class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
  <div class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl text-[#2B2B2B] tracking-tight mb-4 -ml-1">Blog</h1>
    <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
      Physics deep-dives, coding experiments, and reflections on the intersections of art and literature.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-12">
    <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-xs font-medium rounded-full">All Entries</span>
    <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-surface-container text-on-surface-variant text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-secondary-container transition-colors cursor-pointer">Physics</span>
    <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-surface-container text-on-surface-variant text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-secondary-container transition-colors cursor-pointer">Computational</span>
    <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-surface-container text-on-surface-variant text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-secondary-container transition-colors cursor-pointer">Philosophy</span>
  </div>

  <section class="space-y-1 w-full">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="group relative py-11 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-surface-container-low px-4 -mx-4 rounded-lg">
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="block">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline gap-2 md:gap-8">
          <time class="text-xs font-label tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant opacity-60 uppercase shrink-0 w-32">{{ post.date | dateString }}</time>
          <div class="flex-grow">
            <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#2B2B2B] group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-3">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </article>
    {% else %}
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant py-12">Under development — check back soon.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>

  <div class="mt-24 mb-32 flex justify-center">
    <button class="font-label text-sm text-secondary hover:text-primary flex items-center gap-2 group transition-colors">
      View Older Thoughts
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
    </button>
  </div>
</main>
